high_descs: Turn to your right and cross the room to the toilet.
Pick up the bar of soap from the back of the toilet.
Take the bar of soap to the sink on your left.
Rinse the bar of soap off in the sink.
Go to the green wastebasket to the right of the sink.
Throw the soap away in the wastebasket.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a rinsed bar of soap into a green wastebasket.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the toilet to the left.
Take the soap from the back of the toilet.
Turn left and go to the sink.
Wash the soap in the sink.
Go to the waste basket to the right.
Put the soap in the waste basket.
anns.task_desc: Put clean soap in a waste basket.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the green bin in between the sink and toilet to your left.
Pick up the pink bar soap inside the bin.
Put the bar soap in the sink, rinse it off, and pick it back up.
Turn right and head towards the bin on your left.
Place the soap back in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Clean the bar soap inside the green bin.
